about.description:
Rich is a Python library for rich text and beautiful formatting
in the terminal.The Rich API makes it easy to add color and style to
terminal output. Rich can also render pretty tables, progress bars,
markdown, syntax highlighted source code, tracebacks, and more — out
of the box.
about.summary: Rich is a Python library for rich text and beautiful formatting in the terminal.

raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "rich" %}
{% set version = "10.9.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ba285f1c519519490034284e6a9d2e6e3f16dc7690f2de3d9140737d81304d22

build:
  skip: true  # [py<=36 and win]
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - poetry >=1.0.10
    - poetry-core
  run:
    - colorama >=0.4.0,<0.5.0
    - commonmark >=0.9.0,<0.10.0
    - dataclasses >=0.7,<0.8  # [py>=36 and py<37]
    - pygments >=2.6.0,<3.0.0
    - python
    - typing_extensions >=3.7.4,<4.0.0

test:
  imports:
    - rich
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/willmcgugan/rich
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Rich is a Python library for rich text and beautiful formatting in the terminal.

  description: |
    Rich is a Python library for rich text and beautiful formatting 
    in the terminal.The Rich API makes it easy to add color and style to 
    terminal output. Rich can also render pretty tables, progress bars, 
    markdown, syntax highlighted source code, tracebacks, and more — out 
    of the box.
  doc_url: https://rich.readthedocs.io/en/latest/
  dev_url: https://github.com/willmcgugan/rich

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jan-janssen
    - willmcgugan
